/**
 * The `spec.IBaseType` interface represents the specification of an action type.
 *
 * @name pentaho.type.action.spec.IBaseType
 * @interface
 * @extends pentaho.type.spec.IValueType
 */

/**
 * Indicates if the action is synchronous.
 *
 * When unspecified, inherits the value of the ancestor action type.
 * The root action type's value is `true`.
 *
 * If a {@link Nully} value is specified, it is ignored.
 * If a non-boolean value is specified, it is converted to boolean by passing it to the `Boolean` function.
 *
 * @name isSync
 * @memberOf pentaho.type.action.spec.IBaseType#
 * @type {boolean}
 */
